<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('../partials/head') %>
</head>

<body class="font-[Heebo] text-white bg-black">

    <!-- ================= HEADER ================= -->
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>


        <!-- ================= HERO ================= -->
        <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center pt-28 pb-16">

            <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
                <img src="/images/background/slider-image-2.webp" class="w-full h-full object-cover" fetchpriority="high">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/70"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 space-y-10">

                <!-- HERO CARD -->
                <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-8 lg:px-8 lg:py-12
                        bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md
                        rounded-2xl border border-white/20
                        text-center text-white shadow-2xl">
                    <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Infrastructure</h1>
                    <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-200">
                        Sanjeevani Kaya Shodhan Sansthan is thoughtfully designed to support natural healing,
                        comfort, and inner calm through a perfect blend of nature and modern wellness facilities.
                    </p>

                </div>
                <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 lg:px-4 lg:py-12">
                    <!-- IMAGE -->
                    <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl border border-white/20">
                        <img src="/images/treatment/physiotherapist-a.jpeg"
                            alt="Serene Nature Rich Campus at Sanjeevani" class="w-full h-80 object-cover">
                    </div>

                    <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 py-8">Serene & Nature-Rich Campus</h2>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 text-lg">
                        <li><strong>Green Healing Environment:</strong> Lush greenery with open spaces that promote
                            calmness
                            and
                            recovery.
                        </li>
                        <li><strong>Pollution-Free Campus:</strong> Noise-free surroundings supporting mental peace.
                        </li>
                        <li><strong>Healing Gardens & Walkways:</strong> Designed for gentle movement and
                            mindfulness.
                        </li>
                        <li><strong>Natural Light & Fresh Air:</strong> Architecture that enhances circulation and
                            vitality.
                        </li>
                    </ul>


                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">Clinical & Therapy Infrastructure</h2>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 text-lg">
                        <li><strong>Naturopathy Treatment Units:</strong> Dedicated spaces for detox and natural
                            therapies.
                        </li>
                        <li><strong>Hydrotherapy & Bath Therapy Section:</strong> Fully equipped water-based healing
                            units.
                        </li>
                        <li><strong>Massage & Physical Therapy Rooms:</strong> Designed for comfort and therapeutic
                            effectiveness.</li>
                        <li><strong>Ayurveda & Panchakarma Units:</strong> Traditional setups following authentic
                            protocols.
                        </li>
                        <li><strong>Acupressure & Physiotherapy Areas:</strong> Focused on pain relief and
                            functional
                            recovery.
                        </li>
                        <li><strong>Medical Consultation Rooms:</strong> Hygienic and private assessment spaces.
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">Yoga & Meditation Facilities</h2>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 text-lg">
                        <li><strong>Spacious Yoga Halls:</strong> Well-ventilated areas for group and individual
                            practice.
                        </li>
                        <li><strong>Meditation & Pranayama Zones:</strong> Quiet spaces for inner balance.</li>
                        <li><strong>Natural Flooring & Ambience:</strong> Enhancing grounding and focus.</li>
                        <li><strong>Dedicated Practice Areas:</strong> Separate zones for therapy-based sessions.
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">Residential & Stay Facilities</h2>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 text-lg">
                        <li><strong>Comfortable Accommodation:</strong> Clean and well-maintained rooms.</li>
                        <li><strong>Flexible Stay Options:</strong> Single and shared rooms available.</li>
                        <li><strong>Peaceful Living Environment:</strong> Supports deep healing and rest.</li>
                        <li><strong>Recovery-Focused Design:</strong> Rooms designed for relaxation and renewal.
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">Dining & Nutrition Area</h2>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 text-lg">
                        <li><strong>Wellness Dining Hall:</strong> Dedicated space for mindful eating.</li>
                        <li><strong>Satvik & Therapeutic Meals:</strong> Prepared as per treatment protocols.</li>
                        <li><strong>Fresh & Hygienic Food:</strong> Naturally cooked with quality ingredients.</li>
                        <li><strong>Personalized Nutrition:</strong> Diet plans aligned with individual therapy
                            needs.
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-10 mb-4">Support Facilities</h2>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 text-lg">
                        <li><strong>24/7 Utilities:</strong> Continuous water and electricity supply.</li>
                        <li><strong>Comfort Amenities:</strong> Hot water, geysers, and climate support.</li>
                        <li><strong>Housekeeping & Laundry:</strong> Regular cleaning and maintenance.</li>
                        <li><strong>Secure Parking:</strong> Safe vehicle parking within campus.</li>
                        <li><strong>High-Speed Wi-Fi:</strong> Available for essential communication.</li>
                        <li><strong>Safety Lockers:</strong> Secure storage for personal belongings.</li>
                    </ul>


                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ================= FOOTER ================= -->
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>


